e with thee -well, they were false to God [Himself] ere this: but He gave [the believers] mastery over them. And God is all-knowing, wise.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1231.mp3","surahId":8,"words":[{"id":60194,"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِن","translation":"এবং যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/008_071_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60195,"position":2,"arabic":"يُرِيدُوا۟","translation":"তারা চায়","audioUrl":"wbw/008_071_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60196,"position":3,"arabic":"خِيَانَتَكَ","translation":"তোমার সাথে বিশ্বাসভঙ্গ করতে","audioUrl":"wbw/008_071_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60197,"position":4,"arabic":"فَقَدْ","translation":"তবে নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/008_071_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60198,"position":5,"arabic":"خَانُوا۟","translation":"তারা বিশ্বাসভঙ্গ করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/008_071_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60199,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহর সাথে","audioUrl":"wbw/008_071_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60200,"position":7,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/008_071_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60201,"position":8,"arabic":"قَبْلُ","translation":"পূর্ব","audioUrl":"wbw/008_071_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60202,"position":9,"arabic":"فَأَمْكَنَ","translation":"অতঃপর শক্তিশালী করে দিয়েছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/008_071_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60203,"position":10,"arabic":"مِنْهُمْ ۗ","translation":"উপর তাদের  (তোমাদেরকে)","audioUrl":"wbw/008_071_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60205,"position":11,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","translation":"এবং আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/008_071_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60206,"position":12,"arabic":"عَلِيمٌ","translation":"সবকিছু জানেন","audioUrl":"wbw/008_071_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60207,"position":13,"arabic":"حَكِيمٌ","translation":"প্রজ্ঞাময়","audioUrl":"wbw/008_071_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60208,"position":14,"arabic":"٧١","translation":"(৭১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":72,"arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ وَهَاجَرُوا۟ وَجَٰهَدُوا۟ بِأَمْوَٰلِهِمْ وَأَنفُسِهِمْ فِى سَبِيلِ ٱللَّهِ وَٱلَّذِينَ ءَاوَوا۟ وَّنَصَرُوٓا۟ أُو۟لَٰٓئِكَ بَعْضُهُمْ أَوْلِيَآءُ بَعْضٍۢ ۚ وَٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ وَلَمْ يُهَاجِرُوا۟ مَا لَكُم مِّن وَلَٰيَتِهِم مِّن شَىْءٍ حَتَّىٰ يُهَاجِرُوا۟ ۚ وَإِنِ ٱسْتَنصَرُوكُمْ فِى ٱلدِّينِ فَعَلَيْكُمُ ٱلنَّصْرُ إِلَّا عَلَىٰ قَوْمٍۭ بَيْنَكُمْ وَبَيْنَهُم مِّيثَٰقٌۭ ۗ وَٱللَّهُ بِمَا تَعْمَلُونَ بَصِيرٌۭ","translation":"BEHOLD, as for those who have attained to faith, and who have forsaken the domain of evil and are striving hard, with their possessions and their lives, in God's cause, as well as those who shelter and succour [them] - these are [truly] the friends and protectors of one another. But as for those who have come to believe without having migrated [to your country] - you are in no wise responsible for their protection until such a time as they migrate [to you]. Yet, if they ask you for succour against religious persecution, it is your duty to give [them] this succour-except against a people between whom and yourselves there is a covenant: for God sees all that you do.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1232.mp3","surahId":8,"words":[{"id":60467,"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/008_072_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60468,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/008_072_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60469,"position":3,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوا۟","translation":"ঈমান এনেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/008_072_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60470,"position":4,"arabic":"وَهَاجَرُوا۟","translation":"ও হিজরত করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/008_072_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60471,"position":5,"arabic":"وَجَـٰهَدُوا۟","translation":"ও জিহাদ করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/008_072_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60472,"position":6,"arabic":"بِأَمْوَٰلِهِمْ",